<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Your New Subscription!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Your New Subscription!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for subscribing to our WhatsApp Tool! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        
        <h2>Your Subscription Details:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Plan: {{planName}}</li>
            <li>Expiry Date: {{endDate}}</li>
        </ul>

        <p>You can now access all the features included in your plan. Here's what you can do next:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Set up your WhatsApp connection</li>
            <li>Configure your auto-reply settings</li>
            <li>Start managing your groups</li>
        </ul>

        <a href="{{invoiceUrl}}" class="button">View Invoice</a>

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The WhatsApp Tool Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 